snippet.title: Dodo Kids
snippet.description:
Introducing Dodo Kids! A NEW channel on YouTube that’s all about positivity from the most loved animal brand in the world.

Dodo Kids is THE place for kids (preschoolers and up) who love animals and who love to see furry, funny, heartwarming, inspiring, exciting and playful animal stories.


On this channel you will:

Hang out with Roman, a kid who’s rescued SO MANY dogs!

Meet Khula the rhino and his best friend - a goat named Imbuzi!

Sing and dance with Butterfly Guy (a guy who REALLY likes butterflies). 

See REAL baby foxes being rescued. 

Meet kittens, puppies, lambs, goats, cows, dolphins, rhinos, turtles, old dogs, young dogs, baby chicks, birds, monkeys, deer and ALL the other animal stars from The Dodo. 

Come back every week for NEW Dodo Kids videos! And tell us about your favorite animal in the comments!
